\id PHP
\h Filipenses
\toc1 Kart daa bzej Páblona' na' bseḻeen lao beṉ'ka' nonḻilall' Jesucrístona' yell Filípoza'
\toc2 Filipenses
\toc3 Fil.
\mt1 Kart daa bzej Páblona' na' bseḻeen lao beṉ'ka' nonḻilall' Jesucrístona' yell Filípoza'
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nad' Pablo na'ch Timotewi naknto' wen llin c̱he Jesucrístona', chwapnto' chiox yog'le, le' lle'le yell Filípoza', le' nakle lall' na' Chioza' daa nonḻilall'le Cristo Jesúza'. Na' ḻekzka' chwapnto' chiox beṉ'ka' chgoo xṉezi xshin Chioza' ladjlena' na' beṉ'ka' chaklen ḻegake'.\fig Yell Filípoza' llian cho'a nisdo'na'.|src="48_HK00363B.TIF" size="COL" ref="Filipenses 1:1"\fig*
\v 2 Chios, beena' nak X̱acho len X̱ancho Jesucrístona' gaklenshgagake' le' na' wzoagake' le' mbalaz.
\p 
\v 3 Ka ka chjadinid' le' cho'a Chios c̱ha'na' yeḻ' chox̱ken.
\v 4 Na' toshiizi choe'ḻwillee kon yeḻ' xaba kat' chṉabidee gaklene' yog'le,
\v 5 daa lenle chonle nad' txen, dezd ka wyajḻe'le ax̱t ṉaa, kwenc̱he ides dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Jesucrístona'.
\v 6 Ṉezyeṉ'id' Chios, beena' wzolo chone' to dii wen ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'lena', gone' kwenc̱he yiyoll yido yiyakle ka chazlallee kat' illin lla yila' Jesucrístona'.
\v 7 Na' chiyaḻ'kz yibaid' ka chjadinid' le', ḻa' toshiizi yoole ḻoo yic̱hjlall'dawaani. Na' ḻa'kzi dia' lillyani wa choe'len' beṉ' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Jesucrístona' kwenc̱he gakbe'gakile' nakan dill' ḻi na' shajḻe'gake' c̱heyin, ṉezid' toshiizi chaklenle nad' lo llinna' daa ben Chioza' lall' na' gon' yeḻ' beṉ' wen c̱he'na'.
\v 8 Chioza' ṉez nḻe'ile' ka chakid' yog'le kon ka chaki Cristo Jesúza' le'.
\v 9 Kat' choe'ḻwill' Chioza', chṉabidee zizikli yisgolche' yeḻ' chaki c̱helena', na' goṉche' le' yeḻ' sin'na' len yeḻ' chajniina'
\v 10 kwenc̱he gakbe'ile daa nakch wen na' ka' soale do yic̱hj do lall'le na' bibi doḻ' gaple kat' yiyed Crístona'.
\v 11 Na' Jesucrístona' gaklene' le' gonle ḻega beṉ' ḻi beṉ' shao' kwenc̱he sho' Chioza' balaaṉ na' we'la'o beṉ' ḻe'.
\p 
\v 12 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', cheenid' iṉezile diiki ba gok c̱ha' goklenlan kwenc̱he bdesch dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Jesucrístona', na' bi bizogakin wsej wllongakan.
\v 13 Ḻa' ṉaa yog'ḻoḻ soldadka' lle' ni na' nochlə beṉ' yoblə lle' do ni ṉezgakile' dia' lillyani daa chonḻilallaa Crístona'.
\v 14 Na' daa dia' lillyani, zan beṉ' bish'choka' ba wloolall'gake' chongake' lall'chog choe'gake' xtill' Chioza' na' bi chllebgake'.
\p 
\v 15 Dii ḻi baḻgake' choe'gake' xtill' Crístona' daa chakxe'zgakile' nad' na' daa cheenzgakile' gonchgake' ka nad'. Per zoakz beṉ' chone'n do yic̱hj do lallee.
\v 16 Beṉ'kin chongake'n daa chakgakile' nad' na' daa ṉezgakile' Chioza' ba nzoe' nad' kwenc̱he wi'a dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Jesucrístona'.
\v 17 Na' beṉ'ka' zi shkwen choe'gake' xtill' Crístona' daa cheenzgakile' gonchgake' ka nad', na' aga chongake'n do lall'gake'. Na' chakzgakile' daa chongake' ka' gakyeshid' daa nej' lillyani.
\v 18 Per aga bi chon daa c̱ha' shi do lall'gaken' chongake'n wa aga do lall'gaken'; kon daa choe'lgake' xtill' Crístona', daalan chibaid'.
\p Na' zizikli yibachid'
\v 19 daa ṉezid' wichej' wen lao yog' diiki chak c̱ha' daa chṉable c̱ha' lao Chioza' na' daa chaklen Espíritu c̱he Jesucrístona' nad'.
\v 20 Na' toshiizi non' lez Chioza' gaklene' nad' kwenc̱he bi sia' yeḻ' zto', san ṉaa na' toshiizi gon' kwenc̱he sho' Crístona' balaaṉ, ḻaa ibanch' wa ḻaa guet'.
\v 21 Ḻa' shi ibanch', gonchkz' daa cheeni Crístona'; na' shi guet', de to banez c̱ha'.
\v 22 Shi dech yeḻ' mban c̱ha', gonchkz' xshin Crístona' kwenc̱he beṉ' zanch gombia'gake'ne'. Na' bi ṉezid' non nakch wen.
\v 23 Chonan lallj iṉia' non nakch wen: to cheenid' guet' kwenc̱he lljazoalen' Crístona', na' naktechlan wen.
\v 24 Per chonchan byen ibanch' ni c̱hele.
\v 25 Chakid' nakchan wen ibanch' kwenc̱he gaklench' le' gakchachle gonḻilall'le Crístona' na' yiba yizakchile daa nonḻilall'lene'.
\v 26 Na' kat' ile'ile nad' ladjlena' sto shii, ḻe yiba yizakile we'la'ole Cristo Jesúza'.
\p 
\v 27 Naktez gak, ḻi se wṉeyi wsa'to c̱hele wen ḻega beṉ' chajḻe' c̱he dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Crístona' kwenc̱he ḻaa yidwia' le' wa ḻaa yenzid' xtill'le, iṉezid' ni zoac̱hec̱hle nx̱enilall'le Crístona' na' nakle toz chonle ga zeelo chakle kwenc̱he shajḻe' beṉ' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he'na',
\v 28 na' bi gall illebzle beṉ'ka' chakzi' chakzbani le'. Na' daa gonle ka', wli'n kwiayi'chokzgaken', na' le' yilale, ḻa' Chioza' bi wi'e latj kwiayi'le.
\v 29 Ḻa' Chioza' goklene' le' kwenc̱he beṉlilall'le Crístona', na' ḻekzka' chaklene' le' lo yeḻ' zak'zi'ka' chen chle'ile daa nonḻilall'lene'.
\v 30 Ba chsak'zi'gake' le' ka ble'ile bsak'zi'gake' nad' daa chyix̱ji'a xtill' Crístona', na' ṉezkzile ka'kzə ni chak c̱ha'.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Daa nakle Crístona' toz, yeḻ' goklen c̱he'na' chtipan lall'le, na' yeḻ' chaki c̱he'na' chonan ka soale mbalaz, na' Espíritu c̱he'na' zoalenkze' le', na' lall'do'lena' nakan lall'do' yesh'.
\v 2 Daan, ḻi gak toz, ḻi gaki ljwell-le ganga, na' toz ka dii sele wṉeyi, na' toz ka dii selall'le, kwenc̱he yiba yizakchid' ni c̱hele.
\v 3 Bibi sele wṉeyi c̱he tozle wa kwenc̱he gon kwinle beṉ' choo beṉ' xen, san ḻi gonan kon yeḻ' gax̱jlall', ḻi goni beṉ' ka beṉ' zak'chi ka le'.
\v 4 Ni tole bi chiyaḻ' c̱hiljzle dii nak to banez c̱hezle, san ḻekzka' ḻi gon ka si' beṉ' yoblə banez.
\p 
\v 5 Ḻi se wṉeyi gonle ka ben Crístona'.
\q1 
\v 6 Ḻa'kzi nake' Chios,
\q1 bzanile' yeḻ' wṉabia' c̱he'na' na' balaaṉ c̱he'na' daa naplene' X̱e' Chioza',
\q1 
\v 7 na' bzoe' ka'lə daa naki c̱he',
\q1 na' ben kwine' ka to beṉ' bi zakii,
\q1 na' golje' goke' to beṉ' de beli chen.
\q1 
\v 8 Na' ka ba nake' beṉ' yell-lio, bḻex̱j yic̱hje'
\q1 bene' kon ka wna Chioza'
\q1 ax̱t bi'e latj betgake'ne' ḻee yag cruza'.
\q1 
\v 9 Daan, Chioza' wlo'ene' to balaaṉ xen inlleb daa ḻiizelozi zak'chi,
\q1 na' bzoe'ne' nake' x̱an yog'ḻoḻte dii de,
\q1 
\v 10 kwenc̱he yog' beṉ' lle' yabana', na' lo yell-lioni, na' xan yell-lioni
\q1 kat' yengakile' le Jesúza' wc̱hek' xibe'ka' lawe'na'.
\q1 
\v 11 Na' yog'ḻoḻ beṉ' we'gake' dill' nan Jesucrístona' nake' X̱ancho
\q1 na' daa gongake' ka' sho' X̱acho Chioza' balaaṉ.
\p 
\v 12 Daan, le' beṉ' bish'dawaa na' le' beṉ' zandawaa, kon ka ba benkzle toshiizi bzoale dill' kana' wzoalen' le', ḻi we'ḻ-lall'ch gakchle beṉ' wizoa dill' ṉaa bich zoa' ladjlena'. Ḻi gall illeb Chioza', beena' bisla le', na' ḻi gon ka dii le gonle daa cheenile'.
\v 13 Ḻa' Chioza'kzan chone' kwenc̱he chalj ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'lena' gonle dii wenna' daa chaklallee gonle, na' ḻekzka' chaklene' le' kwenc̱he chonlen.
\p 
\v 14 Na' yog'ḻoḻ daa gonle, ḻi gonan do yic̱hj do lall'le, na' bi gaklleshile ni bi gakguedzle,
\v 15 kwenc̱he beṉ' malka' lle' yell-lioni, beṉ'ka' nxiṉj yic̱hjlall'do'eka', gakbe'gakile' bibi dii mal chonle, na' kono bi gak iṉa c̱hele. Na' gaktole beṉ' bibi doḻ' c̱heyin de, ḻega beṉ' nak dowalj xiiṉ Chios. Na' gakle to beeni' lawe'ka', ka beljdo'ka' chey cheeni',
\v 16 daa chzoac̱hec̱hle chzenagle c̱he cho'a xtill' Chioza' daa nsa' yeḻ' mban. Na' shi ka' gonle, kat'ka' yila' Crístona' de dii gonan ka yibaid' daa bi bendadz' xshin Chioza' ladjlena'.
\v 17 Daa chzani kwinle sak'zi'le kwenc̱he gonle daa cheeni Chioza' ṉaa nonḻilall'le Crístona', zaklebin daa chzani beṉ' choe' Chioza' kwenc̱he choe'laweene'. Na' daa chzanid' kwin' witgake' nad' daa chon' xshin Crístona', zaklebin ka daa chlaljgake' lao daa chzani beṉ' choe' Chioza'. Na' ḻa'kzi ax̱t witgake' nad', chiba chizakid' na' cheenid' yiba yizaklenile nad'.
\v 18 Ḻi yiba yizakleni nad', na' ḻi soa mbalaz ka zoa'.
\p 
\v 19 Non' lez X̱ancho Jesúza' wi'e latj yobzə wseḻaa Timotewa' gana' zoale, kwenc̱he yibaid' ka yiyede' iṉe' chak wen c̱hele.
\v 20 Kochno zoa sto c̱ha' ka ḻe', ḻa' tochga ḻen' zelene' nad' wṉeyi do yic̱hj do lallee gak wen c̱hele.
\v 21 Ḻa' beṉ'ki sto zoalen nad', c̱he kwinzgake' zegake' wṉeyi na' bi zegake' wṉeyi daa cheeni Jesucrístona'.
\v 22 Per ba ṉezkzile ka wen nsa' c̱he Timotewa' na' ka ba goklene' nad' ba be'nto' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Crístona'. Ba goklene' nad' ka beṉ' chaklen x̱ayin.
\v 23 Daan, kat' ba ṉezid' nakan gak c̱ha', lii wseḻ'tia'ne' gana' zoale.
\v 24 Na' nx̱enlallaa X̱anchona' ḻekzka' yob yidwia' le' kwinkz'.
\p 
\v 25 Na' ṉaa chakid' chonan byen yiseḻaa beṉ' bish'cho Epafrodítoni, beeni nonlene' nad' txen chdiḻ-lennto' dii mala' daa chonnto' xshin Chioza', beeni bseḻ'le kwenc̱he gaklene' nad' lao dii chyallj chc̱hinid'.
\v 26 Cheenchgaile' ile'ile' le', na' ḻe chakyeshile' daa wṉezile we'ile'.
\v 27 Na' dii ḻicha zi lat'zə ki wite', per Chioza' biyesh'lallile'ne' biyakile'. Na' aga tozen' biyesh'lallile', san lenan' kwenc̱he bi gakyesh'chid'.
\v 28 Daan chiseḻaane' laolena' dopiyenzə kwenc̱he yibaile' daa yile'ilene' sto shii, na' nad' bich gakyesh'tekid' c̱hele.
\v 29 Ḻi yilebgache' kon yeḻ' chiba chizaki daa nake' cho' txen nonḻilall'cho X̱anchona'. Na' ḻi gap balaaṉ yog'ḻoḻ beṉ'ka' chon ka chone'.
\v 30 Ḻa' zi lat'zə ki wite' daa chone' xshin Crístona'. Bzoe' dii nxoll yeḻ' mban c̱he'na' goktgui bidyaklene' nad' bidyene' diika' bi gok gonle.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Na' ṉaa, le' beṉ' bish'dawaa na' le' beṉ' zandawaa, ḻi yiba yizaki daa ba nonḻilall'le X̱anchona'. Nad' bi chak zedid' wzej' le' dii yoblə diika' ba wniakz' le' daa ṉezid' waklenan le'.
\v 2 Ḻi wsak' bi wzenagle c̱he beṉ' malka', beṉ'ka' nazə chonan byen wc̱hogtekzə kwerp c̱hechona' sho'cho seṉ daa le circuncisión.
\v 3 Ḻa' cho'yeṉ'lan nakcho dowalj beṉ'ka' yoo seṉ, cho' choe'la'ocho Chioza' daa yoo Espíritu c̱he'na' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'chona' na' chiba chizakicho daa nakcho Cristo Jesúza' txen. Na' bi noncho lez daa goni kwerp c̱hechoni gaklenan gakcho beṉ' wen lao Chioza'.
\v 4 Nia' ka' ḻa'kzi de dii zan dii gak wx̱enilallaa c̱he kwin' daa gonan ka ile'shii Chioza' nad'. Shi no chakzi de dii gak wx̱enilallee c̱he kwine' daa gonan ka ile'shii Chioza'ne', ¿alechlin nad'?
\v 5 Ka gokid' x̱on' lla, wloogake' kwerp c̱ha'ni seṉ daa le circuncisión. Nak' beṉ' Israel, na' golj' lo dia c̱he dii Benjamínna', na' nak' dowalj beṉ' hebreo ka x̱axṉa'ka', na' bsedyeṉaa ley c̱hento'na' na' bzenag' c̱heyin, na' benlen' fariseoka' txen.
\v 6 Daa ḻe wzechga' wṉeyi ley c̱he Chioza', ax̱t gokid' chon' ka cheeni Chioza' daa bc̱hi' bsakaa beṉ'ka' chonḻilall'gake' Jesúza'. Na' ben' kon ka na leya', na' aga no gok iṉa bi ben' ka nan.
\v 7 Kana'n gokid' ḻe zak'chgayi yog' diika', per ṉaa, daa ba nonḻilallaa Crístona', chakbe'id' bibi zak'gakan.
\v 8 Na' dii ḻi ṉezid' bibi de dii zak'chi ka daa ba nombia' Cristo Jesúza', beena' nak X̱an'. Na' daa ḻe chakidee, bich nx̱enilallaa yog' diika' gokid' ḻe zak'chga, san ba nongaka'n ka beb kwenc̱he gombia'ch' Crístona'
\v 9 na' gakee txen. Aga daa chon' daa na leyan' nak' beṉ' ḻi beṉ' shao' lao Chioza', san daa nonḻilallaa Crístonan', ḻa' beṉ'ka' chonḻilall'gake' Crístona', Chioza' chiyone' ḻegake' beṉ' ḻi beṉ' shao'.
\v 10 Cheenid' gombia' Crístona' na' yeḻ' wak c̱he'na' ka daa bli'e kana' bibane' ladj beṉ' wetka', na' cheenid' izanid' kwin' gak c̱ha' ka gok c̱he' daa wdie' yeḻ' zak'zi'ka' na' wite'.
\v 11 Na' ka', non' lez idoḻaa yisban Chioza' nad' ladj beṉ' wetka'.
\p 
\v 12 Bi nia' ba nombi'ane' kwasḻoḻ wa ba chon' kwasḻoḻ ka chazlallee. Per ni chon' ka dii le kwenc̱he gak gona'n, ḻa' ni c̱he ḻennan' gox wṉab Cristo Jesúza' nad'.
\v 13 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', bi nia' ba chon' kwasḻoḻ ka chazlallee. Per de to dii chon', bich zia' wṉeyi c̱he diika' ba wde, san chon' to dii byen kwenc̱he idoḻid' dii wenna' zi' za'.
\v 14 Ni chon' ka dii le kwenc̱he yillin' gana' ikaa daa goṉ Chioza' nad'. Ḻa' ni c̱heyinnan' gox wṉabe' nad' kwenc̱he nak' Crístona' txen.
\p 
\v 15 Na' kan' chiyaḻ' secho wṉeyi yog'ḻoḻcho, cho' ba nakchacho chonḻilall'chone'. Na' shi bi zelen wṉeyi Chioza'kzə wzajniile'n le'.
\v 16 Na' daa llialote chiyaḻ' soatezi soacho goncho kon ka ba bzajnii Chioza' cho'.
\p 
\v 17 Le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', ḻi wsa'to c̱hele ka nsa' c̱ha', na' ka nsa' c̱he beṉ'ka' chon kon ka ba bliinto' le' gonle.
\v 18 Zan shii ba wnia' le', na' ṉaa ax̱t chakyeshid' nia' le' dga sto shii, zan beṉ' chongake' ka bibi zakii daa wit Crístona' ḻee yag cruza' daa bi nsa' c̱hegake' wen.
\v 19 Wllin lla kwiayi' beṉ'ki daa choe'la'ogake' toz daa chṉab beli chen c̱he'ka', na' chep cha'lall'lgake' c̱heyi daa chongake' lwaayi dii nan yido'gakile'. Kon lillinzi daa de yell-lioni zegake' wṉeyi.
\v 20 San cho', yabanan' nak lallcho. Na' nan' ziza' X̱ancho Jesucrístona', beena' chbezcho yisle' cho' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'cho.
\v 21 Ḻen' yishee kwerp c̱hechoki, diiki gooll' iteb, kwenc̱he yiyakan ka kwerp c̱he'na' daa ḻe zakii. Na' gone'n kon yeḻ' wak c̱he'na' daa chṉabia'lene' lao yog'ḻoḻte dii de.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Le' beṉ' bish'dawaa na' le' beṉ' zandawaa, ḻe chakid' le', na' chzelall'chgaid' ile'id' le', na' chiba chizakid' daa nonḻilall'le Crístona', na' ni c̱hele le' de to dii yizi'a banez. Ḻi soac̱hec̱h gonḻilall'le X̱anchona'.
\p 
\v 2 Chat'yoid' Evódiana' len Síntiquena' yizoagake' wen daa nakgake' X̱anchona' txen.
\v 3 Na' li' nako' nad' txen do yic̱hj do lalloo choncho xshin Chioza', chat'yoid' li', gaklengacho' beṉ' zanchoki. Ḻa' ḻe ba bllaglogaken' goklengake' nad' be'nto' dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Jesucrístona', len Cleméntena' na' beṉ'ka' sto benlench nad' xshin Chioza'. Ba da' lie'ka' ḻee libr c̱he Chioza' gana' da' le beṉ'ka' napgake' yeḻ' mban zejḻi kaṉi.
\p 
\v 4 Ḻi yiba yizaki toshiizi daa nakle X̱ancho Crístona' txen. Na' sto shii nia' le': ¡ḻi yiba yizaki!
\v 5 Ḻi wsa' c̱hele xochi kwenc̱he yog' beṉ' gakbe'gakile' nakle beṉ' wen. Ba zoa gao yiyed X̱anchona'.
\p 
\v 6 Bi kwekzə yic̱hjle bittez dii chak c̱hele, san ḻi we'ḻwill Chioza' na' ḻi gonan lall' nee, na' ḻi wi'e yeḻ' chox̱ken.
\v 7 Na' gone' ka soale mbalaz ax̱t kono shajniikzi bic̱he zoale ka'. Na' yeḻ' zoa mbalaza' wsol wṉitan dii zeda' de ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'leka' daa nakle Cristo Jesúza' txen.
\p 
\v 8 Na' le' beṉ' bish' na' le' beṉ' zan', daa zeelote ṉaa, ḻi se wṉeyi c̱heyi daa nak dii ḻi, c̱he yog'ḻoḻte dii chidoḻ' gapcho balaaṉ, c̱he yog'ḻoḻ daa nak dii ḻi dii shao', c̱he yog'ḻoḻ dii bibi dii mal nsa'n, c̱he yog' dii wenka' chon ka yibaicho, na' c̱he yog'ḻoḻ dii zeyi c̱heyin nakan wen. Ḻi se wṉeyi c̱he yog'ḻoḻ diiki nak wen, diiki chidoḻ' we'cho xtilliin.
\p 
\v 9 Ḻi gon daa ba bli' bsedid' le' na' daa benile wnia', na' daa ble'ile chon'. Ḻennan' ḻi gon, na' Chios, beena' chon ka soacho mbalaz, soalene' le'.
\p 
\v 10 Chiba chizakchgaid' lao X̱ancho Jesucrístona' daa bachga chizele wṉeyi c̱ha' dii yoblə. Bi nia' ba goḻ-lall'le nad', san bi got' xḻatjinnan' gaklentole nad'.
\v 11 Aga daa chyallj chc̱hinida'n nia' ka', ḻa' ba nzedid' gon' banez ka'k' dii de c̱ha'.
\v 12 Ba ṉezid' bi daa ne' soe' lo yeḻ' yesh', na' ḻekzka' ba ṉezid' bi daa ne' soe' lo yeḻ' wnia'. Ba nzedid' gon' banez bittez dii chak c̱ha', shi neḻj nlla'id' wa shi chbiḻ chdon', shi dechga daa chyallj chc̱hinid' wa shi shlas bibi dekzə.
\v 13 Chzoid' yog'ḻoḻte dii chtiḻ' daa chaklen Crístona' nad'.
\v 14 Per ḻe wen benle daa goklenle nad' lo dii lalljki chtiḻ'.
\p 
\v 15 Na' ṉezkzile kana' bizaa Macedóniana' na' wzoloa' cho'a dill' wen dill' kob c̱he Crístona', totgui le' lle'le Filipoza' beṉle daa byalljid' kwenc̱he ji'a cho'a xtill' Chioza'. Ḻa' ni to beṉ'ka' ba nonḻilall' Crístona' yellka' sto bi goklengake' nad'.
\v 16 Na' kana' wzoa' yell Tesalónicana', zan shii bseḻ'le dii byalljid'.
\v 17 Aga iṉacho chyilj' bi goṉle nad', san cheenlid' gat'ch yeḻ' shao' c̱hele yabana'.
\v 18 Epafrodítoni ba beṉe' nad' daa bseḻ'lenlene', na' ṉaa ba nap' yog'te daa chyalljid' ax̱t ba chichooṉlan. Na' chibayi Chioza' daa bseḻ'len, ka chibaile' diika' chzani beṉ' choe'gake'ne', diika' chḻa'ile' zix̱ sia kat' chzeygake'n lawe'na'.
\v 19 Chios c̱ha'na', beena' nap yog'ḻoḻte dii wen dii shao'ka', goṉe' le' yog'ḻoḻ daa chyalljile daa nakle Cristo Jesúza' txen.
\v 20 Toshiizi chiyaḻ' koocho X̱acho Chioza' balaaṉ. Kan' nakan.
\p 
\v 21 Ḻi wwapsha chiox yog'ḻoḻ beṉ'ka' nak lall' na' Chioza' daa nongake' Cristo Jesúza' txen. Na' ḻekzka' beṉ' bish'choki zoalen nad' ni, chwapgake' le' chiox.
\v 22 Na' yog'ḻoḻte beṉ'ka' nak lall' na' Chioza' ni chwapgake' le' chiox, na' beṉ'ka' chon xshin beṉ' wṉabia' Césara', ḻeyeṉ'gake' chwapgake' le' chiox.
\p 
\v 23 X̱ancho Jesucrístona' soalenshgue' le' na' gaklene' yog'ḻoḻtele. Kan' gakan.
